Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is how the arrangements came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strategy meeting—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to use up your first paycheck right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all this time, I wanted to get some presents or something, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...buy something for yourself as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the first month was only training, you didn't get much, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there were usually issues with the wages, and that we're paid in military scrip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd receive real money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course! That's because our platoon was set up to—!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that is, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fair today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first paycheck and your first day off, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're having all kinds of firsts this week, aren't you, Kanata-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about your occupation and enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:29.14,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,75.333333)}Kanata's Day Off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:29.14,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,441.333333)}Hairdressing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to let Kanata suspect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if we weren't in the middle of nowhere and our supplies weren't always delayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would still never give us actual money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Kanata simply believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best if she stays innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she'll figure out where the money comes from anytime soon, unlike you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, how about we forget our normal occupations as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, there's nothing left but to say you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a problem on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning that one proposition, will you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the sellers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has something caught your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it sells, it will take a lot of time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it like that, we're a little short on manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't give discounts on principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.69,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost is a part of its flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we're saying that we've lost or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just take all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, maybe I'll be able to pull the trigger before you can,{too bad we can't do eastwood's "Do you feel lucky?", lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this time I might just blow a hole in your head just like that hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your punishment for taking us lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Don's souvenirs...{different level of boss here. like, family head vs local boss}{Hmm... "Don" is the best i can think of, since "Big Boss" doesn't seem right...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are worthless if we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! I'm never coming back to this town with those dangerous people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard them.{They're gone - works too, but is just an easy fit in english.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's enough everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, that was exciting.{Could be scary, given the situation.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we deceived them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are grateful for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. If we had gotten involved with the mafia, our business would be doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dog-eat-dog world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, for our part in this act, of course you'll be giving us our due, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please! You're full of jokes, Mikhail-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. It's not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, it's back to business.{Literal, perhaps "all business"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that... why don't you leave those with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the ones who crushed their car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like someone crushed their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a pile of goods from the fair inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I say I bought them, and then we split the profits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we've reached an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This farce is finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were in high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it got out that we're moonshining, we'd have to apologize in a court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monopoly law violation and tax law violation as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worst case, charged with treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a side job handed down to us from our senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Rio never once objected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drink that my mother loved, this calvados...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I found out it was made at the fort...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps it was your mother that guided your assignment to our platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm heading off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very nice, Seiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is your first visit to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pastor is also coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trouble Onee-chan, Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her doing your hair properly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't! I won't let her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always bugging me to do mine! You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't do that, Mishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10.25 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry! I wasn't paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, people like you...{what do you mean YOU PEOPLE? In background, btw.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.31,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they somehow caught wind of the transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Naomi-san! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever had money in my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I say I want it now, I could finally buy it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if someone came and snatched up that dolphin, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone who said they wanted it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just a "what if" situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... If it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'd tell them to give up because dolphins are super scary animals that eat humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hold onto that dolphin until you need it, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd better find presents for everyone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... there's Dad, Mom, Auntie and Uncle, Grandma and Grandpa Warren, Great-Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Auntie Nanae from next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They're selling so many different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Mishio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you buying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she's searching for a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. Have you seen it anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for it, can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm buying presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if there were any wonderful things I could send to my family in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Mishio-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kanata-san, have you seen Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think it was something important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother passed away, all of their belongings were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, it seems that box—a memento from her mother—was also taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time there is a fair in town, she hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my first wages yesterday, so I thought I would send something to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I... we are trying to be Mishio-san's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, if you say Mishio-san is jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it is all because I am not doing an adequate job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama, which is more important, your treasure box, or me?{Cyber suggested puzzle box here.. since it is one. Treasure is literal.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So! How about Treize's famous firecrackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a loud sound! How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm not Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Naomi-san's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that was you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I have 150 yen here! The car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure helped us out, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The payment has already been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naomi-san! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ideograms mean "Beautiful Ear of Rice".{Head, or ear.. depending on how you feel agriculturally}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you carve these onto her seal stamp, she should live a life of happiness like that of a bountiful rice field.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, you've received a good name. Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I try to be her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and intended for her to accept me in her heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am still inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only thing left with your mother's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... want Yumina... to have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san is one of the children taken in by the Church when their families died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, her father was sent to the front lines and never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her family lived on the eastern border of Vingt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the town that was touched by the "Invisible Reaper."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the two of them came to Seize, her mother was showing signs of the illness, and before long...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry I can't do you hair anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:20:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then... And then she told me to give them to the person who was the most important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, when we're separated from those precious to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it feels as if we could die, we will still continue to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can still go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is very sorrowful, but also a display of great willpower.{Make this more poetic if you like}{Sure... sad->sorrowful and good to "a display of great wilpower", although we can use "marvelous" if it seems too long}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, and thank you... Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is already in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked hard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to avoid washing my hair, but a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, senpai. Let me dry your hair for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to feel it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you didn't buy the dolphin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that would be your treat for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai, do you believe in fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.05,0:21:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... I thought that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough of a reward to fill me up!{this line is lolsome}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the idea that everything was decided and set from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence brought forth by someone could go around and around and make a stranger's life grander.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that could be called fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.27,0:22:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Senpai also had a wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Chirping Crickets · Offerings for the Deceased{So for anyone that's wondering about the title, it's those lanterns that get offered down the rivers in paper boats... basically}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:15.00,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,53.333333)\c&H060606&\b1}The Chirping Crickets
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:13.44,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kono sora no kagayaki kimi no mune ni todoiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:13.44,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The luminance of the sky has reached your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:23.47,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}yumemiteta shirabe wa shizukesa no youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:23.47,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The melody I dreamed of was like silence.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.34,0:00:28.52,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no te ga mada yume ni tookutemo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.34,0:00:28.52,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if your hand is still far away in my dreams,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.36,0:00:33.58,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}omoidashiteyou yasashii koe wo
Dialogue: 2,0:00:28.36,0:00:33.58,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I’ll still remember your kind voice
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.37,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}dareka ga kimi no tame utatta shiawase no koto
Dialogue: 3,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.37,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and the happiness that was sung for you.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.11,0:00:55.77,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sora no woto hibike takaku kanashimi wo koete
Dialogue: 4,0:00:46.11,0:00:55.77,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Let the sound of the sky ring high over your sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.54,0:01:06.32,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no me ni utsuru mono wa subete hontou no sekai
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.54,0:01:06.32,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything reflected in your eyes is that of the real world.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.15,0:01:15.79,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}namida sae kimi wo koko ni todomete okenai
Dialogue: 6,0:01:06.15,0:01:15.79,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even tears won’t be able to stop you here.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.52,0:01:27.92,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}furisosogu hikari no naka ashita wo kanadete
Dialogue: 7,0:01:15.52,0:01:27.92,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Amidst the descending lights, you’ll play the song of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's remember our love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou omoikasanete
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.74,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}and play out their importance.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.74,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}taisetsu wo kanadeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.66,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}We were so happy that we cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.66,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}ureshikute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.66,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}It hurt so much that we laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.66,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}itakute waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:22.86,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}But these are all proof that we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:22.86,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}dakedo sonna zenbu ga ikiteru akashi nan desu
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.57,0:23:27.17,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's move forward one step at a time.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.57,0:23:27.17,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}yukkuri aruite yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:28.63,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:33.14,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let me hear the words of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:33.14,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}hitosashi no honne kikasete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.34,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:40.04,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Even if our love and friendship sometimes waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:40.04,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou toki ni yuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:40.34,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}I know, you know, a little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:45.96,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}let's make it echo forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:45.96,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}zutto zutto hibiki aitai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:46.32,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:52.30,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:23:46.05,0:23:52.30,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}arifureteru kotoba de wa tsutaekirenai
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.01,0:23:58.10,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:52.01,0:23:58.10,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}watashitachi no harmony
Dialogue: 2,0:23:58.00,0:24:03.13,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear it? Our harmony!
Dialogue: 3,0:23:58.00,0:24:03.13,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}kikoeru our harmony
